title: Bachmann Bluenet Monitored Power Line Connectors: Voltage, Current and Power
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/bachmann
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the voltage, current, and active and apparent power
 of Bachmann Bluenet Monitored Power Line Connectors (PLCs). It uses the
 NETTRACK-E3METER-SNMP to extract the data from the device.

 Lower and upper warning and critical levels can be configured for this check.
 A non-OK state is triggered according to these levels.

inventory:
 One service is created for each power meter on the device with a non-zero voltage.

item:
 The ID of the power meter.
